io.evitadb:jacoco 2025.6.1 发布, Evita is a specialized database with easy-to-use API for e-commerce systems. Purpose of this research is
		creating fast and scalable engine that handles all complex tasks that e-commerce systems has to deal with on
		daily basis.

		Evita should operate as a fast secondary lookup / search index used by application frontends. We aim for order
		of magnitude better latency (10x faster or better) for common e-commerce tasks than other solutions based on SQL
		or NoSQL databases on the same hardware specification. Evita should not be used for storing and handling primary
		data, and we don't aim for ACID properties nor data corruption guarantees. Evita "index" must be treated
		as something that could be dropped any time and built up from scratch easily again.

        boot、mybatis-plus，在框架原有基础上做了进一步的轻度封装，更加方便使用，针对代码（字段字符串、Mapper、Repository/Service）预生成、数据自动填充（类似JPA中的审计）、关联查询（类似sql中的join）、自动建表、冗余数据自动更新、固定条件等方面通过注解做了增强。

items.title: io.nashid.verify:sdk 2.6.1 发布, UI Improvements to Camera and Instruction Overlay Adjusted the camera background opacity to reduce background distractions during both liveness and ID scanning. Repositioned instruction text overlays and enhanced clarity. NFC Cancel Behaviour Added support for the new feature flag called “Count NFC Cancel.” When enabled, pressing the Cancel button during NFC reading will count as an attempt toward the retry limit. When disabled, canceling will not be counted — allowing users to retry NFC scanning without reducing their available attempts.

items.title: net.linlan.emis:emis-java-backend 1.0.0 发布, 基于JAVA开发的企业级多身份管理系统后端工程，基于Springboot，采用支持 JAVA 1.8最高版本的framework、security，后端数据访问采用Mybatis框架，支持多种数据库一套代码适配，提供脚手架可快速生成Mapper等，在仓库功能上，借鉴主流的SSO和IAM框架，实现统一用户管理。前端提供VUE框架和REACT框架的控制台管理工程、企业个人门户工程和移动端应用扩展。
